name: __EConstantQNormalizationEnum
doc:
EConstantQNormalizationEnum

Enumeration of available normalization schemes for ConstantQ frequency domain windows.

EqualEuclideanNorm: Normalize bands by euclidean norm. Good when using magnitude spectrum.
EqualEnergy: Normalize bands by energy. Good when using power spectrum.
EqualAmplitude: Normalize bands by their maximum values. Will result in relatively strong high frequences because the upper constant Q bands have larger bandwidths.
